title: Airrack's SPRINT to ONE MILLION Subscribers
description:
In the 8th episode of Creator Economics, Reed and Blake chat with one of the most AMBITIOUS creators of 2020: Airrack!  

From his sneak-in stunts, his collabs with huge YouTubers like Logan Paul, and his dramatic shift in content, Airrack is here to win... And winning, is getting one MILLION subs before the end of the year.  

Check out Airrack:  

YT Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyps-v4WNjWDnYRKmZ4BUGw

Twitter: https://twitter.com/airrack

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/airrack/
